{
  "texts": [
    "The issue of security is one of the main difficulties with IoT.",
    "With the enormous number of interconnected devices, there is an increased risk of cyber attacks and data breaches.",
    "IoT devices may connect with one another in a safe, decentralized network thanks to blockchain technology.",
    "By using a distributed ledger, which is maintained by multiple parties, blockchain can create a tamper-proof and transparent record of all transactions and data exchanges.",
    "IoT is facing difficulties in providing secure and private communications due to its large size and widespread deployment."
  ]
}